#: .\fic_mods.json
msgid "Flaregun conversion kit"
msgid_plural "Flaregun conversion kits"
msgstr[0] "信号枪转换套件"

#: .\fic_mods.json
msgid ""
"Replacing several key parts flaregun to convert it to a .40 firearm.  The "
"conversion results in reduced accuracy and increased recoil."
msgstr "替换信号枪的几个关键部件，将其改装为.40口径枪械。改装会导致精度下降和后坐力增加。"

#: .\fic_mods.json
msgid "accessories"
msgstr "配件"

#: .\fic_mods.json
msgid "integral flamethrower"
msgid_plural "integral flamethrowers"
msgstr[0] "内置火焰喷射器"

#: .\fic_mods.json
msgid ""
"This genuine Herostratus flamethrower is ideal for light brush clearing and "
"self-defense."
msgstr "这款正宗的赫罗斯特拉图斯火焰喷射器是清理灌木丛和自卫的理想选择。"

#: .\fic_mods.json
msgid "underbarrel"
msgstr "下挂式"

#: .\fic_mods.json
msgid "E.M.A.S."
msgid_plural "E.M.A.S.s"
msgstr[0] "E.M.A.S."

#: .\fic_mods.json
msgid ""
"ElectroMagnetic Acceleration System is an array of electromagnets attached "
"to the front of the barrel, accelerating any projectile fired to even higher"
" velocities, increasing damage, recoil and reducing accuracy.  It does "
"however drain UPS charges when firing and due to extensive modifications the"
" gun can no longer operate without a UPS."
msgstr ""
"电磁加速系统是一组安装在枪管前端的电磁铁，能将发射的任何弹丸加速到更高速度，从而增加伤害和后坐力，但会降低精度。不过，射击时会消耗UPS电量，且由于大量改装，这把枪在没有UPS的情况下无法再使用。"

#: .\fic_mods.json
msgid "barrel"
msgstr "枪管"

#: .\fic_weapons.json
msgid "Rico 454"
msgid_plural "Rico 454s"
msgstr[0] "里科454"

#: .\fic_weapons.json
msgid ""
"Handmade by a master gunsmith, this deadly accurate and powerful pistol "
"packs a punch with precision, power and flair.  Comes with a one of a kind "
"integrated 40mm IGL."
msgstr "由枪械大师手工制作，这把致命精准且威力强大的手枪集精准、威力和风格于一身。配有独一无二的内置40毫米单兵榴弹发射器。"

#: .\fic_weapons.json
msgid "Boomlighter 454"
msgid_plural "Boomlighter 454s"
msgstr[0] "爆裂者454"

#: .\fic_weapons.json
msgid ""
"Handmade by master gunsmiths at D&B Minneapolis, this deadly accurate and "
"powerful pistol packs a punch with precision, power and flair.  Comes with a"
" one of a kind integrated flamethrower."
msgstr "由明尼阿波利斯D&B的枪械大师手工制作，这把致命精准且威力强大的手枪集精准、威力和风格于一身。配有独一无二的内置火焰喷射器。"

#: .\fic_weapons.json
msgctxt "gun_type_type"
msgid "pistol"
msgstr "手枪"

#: .\fic_weapons.json
msgid "gunsword"
msgid_plural "gunswords"
msgstr[0] "枪刃"

#: .\fic_weapons.json
msgid ""
"A long sharp blade, with two powerful .500 S&W Magnum chambers in the hilt."
"  While chambering big rounds, the barrels are so short it slightly reduces "
"outgoing damage."
msgstr "一把长而锋利的刀刃，刀柄内有两个强大的.500 S&W马格南弹膛。虽然装填大口径弹药，但枪管过短，略微降低了输出伤害。"

#: .\fic_weapons.json
msgid "gunknife"
msgid_plural "gunknives"
msgstr[0] "枪刃匕首"

#: .\fic_weapons.json
msgid ""
"A short but sharp blade, with two powerful .500 S&W Magnum chambers in the "
"grip.  While chambering big rounds, the barrels are so short it slightly "
"reduces outgoing damage."
msgstr "一把短而锋利的刀刃，握柄内有两个强大的.500 S&W马格南弹膛。虽然装填大口径弹药，但枪管过短，略微降低了输出伤害。"

#: .\fic_weapons.json
msgid "FiveO handcannon"
msgid_plural "FiveO handcannons"
msgstr[0] "FiveO手持火炮"

#: .\fic_weapons.json
msgid ""
"Someone crazy thought that the .50 BMG belonged in a pistol.  This massive "
"piece of steel proves otherwise.  The sheer bulk however does make it quite "
"adept at smashing face."
msgstr "某个疯子认为.50 BMG应该用在手枪上。这块巨大的钢铁证明了相反的观点。然而，其庞大的体积确实使其相当擅长砸脸。"

#: .\fic_weapons.json
msgid "H&K MP5A5 EOD"
msgid_plural "H&K MP5A5 EODs"
msgstr[0] "H&K MP5A5 EOD"

#: .\fic_weapons.json
msgid ""
"The Heckler & Koch MP5 is one of the most widely-used submachine guns in the"
" world, and has been adopted by special police forces and militaries alike."
"  This one has been modified with an integrated grenade launcher allowing "
"you to survive the end of days."
msgstr "黑克勒&科赫MP5是世界上使用最广泛的冲锋枪之一，已被特种警察部队和军队采用。这支经过改装，配有内置榴弹发射器，让你能在末日中生存下来。"

#: .\fic_weapons.json
msgid "semi-auto"
msgstr "半自动"

#: .\fic_weapons.json
msgid "3 rd."
msgstr "3 发"

#: .\fic_weapons.json
msgid "auto"
msgstr "自动"

#: .\fic_weapons.json
msgid "Eagle 1776"
msgid_plural "Eagle 1776"
msgstr[0] "雄鹰1776"

#: .\fic_weapons.json
msgid ""
"You see before you a marvel of American engineering: a powerful .44 Magnum "
"submachine gun, made from fine parts assembled in America, including an "
"integral grenade launcher.  Eagle 1776: From the arsenal of freedom!"
msgstr "你眼前的是美国工程学的奇迹：一把强大的.44马格南冲锋枪，由美国组装的优质零件制成，包括一个内置榴弹发射器。雄鹰1776：来自自由武库！"

#: .\fic_weapons.json
msgctxt "gun_type_type"
msgid "smg"
msgstr "冲锋枪"

#: .\fic_weapons.json
msgid "L.T.  carbine"
msgid_plural "L.T.  carbines"
msgstr[0] "L.T.卡宾枪"

#: .\fic_weapons.json
msgid ""
"The Lightning Trail carbine was developed for the riot police to quickly "
"blanket an area with lightning clouds.  While damaging, it is less lethal "
"than live ammunition."
msgstr "闪电轨迹卡宾枪是为防暴警察开发的，能快速用闪电云覆盖一个区域。虽然具有杀伤力，但比实弹的致命性低。"

#: .\fic_weapons.json
msgid "arc cannon"
msgid_plural "arc cannons"
msgstr[0] "电弧炮"

#: .\fic_weapons.json
msgid ""
"The arc cannon fires bolts of lightning arcing between targets in close "
"proximity to each other.  Originally manufactured to fry insects, now it’s "
"been tuned up to fry zombies."
msgstr "电弧炮发射闪电束，在彼此靠近的目标之间形成电弧。最初制造用于电击昆虫，现在经过调整，用于电击僵尸。"

#: .\fic_weapons.json
msgid "M1911 DS"
msgid_plural "M1911 DSs"
msgstr[0] "M1911 DS"

#: .\fic_weapons.json
msgid ""
"The M1911 Darkstalker is a very modified M1911, it has a fully integrated "
"crossbow and added rails.  Professional looking with a ebony black finish, "
"laced with lime green details.  Now they will know why they fear the night."
"  Bat hood sold separately."
msgstr ""
"M1911暗夜潜行者是一把经过大量改装的M1911，拥有完全集成的弩和附加导轨。外观专业，乌木黑色饰面，点缀着青柠绿色细节。现在他们将知道为何畏惧黑夜。蝙蝠兜帽需单独购买。"

#: .\ficmags.json
msgid ".454 6-round speedloader"
msgid_plural ".454 6-round speedloaders"
msgstr[0] ".454 6发快速装弹器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '.454 6-round speedloader'}
#: .\ficmags.json
msgid ""
"This speedloader can hold 6 rounds of .454 and quickly reload a compatible "
"revolver."
msgstr "这个快速装弹器可容纳6发.454子弹，并能快速装填兼容的左轮手枪。"

#: .\ficmags.json
msgid ".454 8-round speedloader"
msgid_plural ".454 8-round speedloaders"
msgstr[0] ".454 8发快速装弹器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '.454 8-round speedloader'}
#: .\ficmags.json
msgid ""
"This speedloader can hold 8 rounds of .454 and quickly reload a compatible "
"revolver."
msgstr "这个快速装弹器可容纳8发.454子弹，并能快速装填兼容的左轮手枪。"

#: .\ficmags.json
msgid "Eagle 1776 magazine"
msgid_plural "Eagle 1776 magazines"
msgstr[0] "Eagle 1776 弹匣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Eagle 1776 magazine'}
#: .\ficmags.json
msgid ""
"An american-made box magazine, designed to deliver 24 .44 Magnum cartridges "
"to the Eagle 1776."
msgstr "一款美国制造的盒式弹匣，设计用于为 Eagle 1776 提供 24 发 .44 马格南子弹。"

#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "DeadLeaves' Fictional Guns"
msgstr "DeadLeaves 的虚构枪械"

#. ~ Description for DeadLeaves' Fictional Guns
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Adds a bunch of rare, fictional weapons."
msgstr "添加了一批稀有的虚构武器。"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid "\"Gun.  Sword.  Gunsword.  Screw bayonets, this is way more awesome.\""
msgstr "\"枪。剑。枪剑。去他的刺刀，这玩意儿酷多了。\""

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"\"Not sure if wielding this thing makes me feel like a bodybuilder or a "
"theoretical physicist.  Both?\""
msgstr "\"不确定挥舞这东西是让我感觉像个健美运动员还是理论物理学家。或许两者都是？\""

#: .\snippets.json
msgid "\"This ain't your grandaddy's .50 cal hand cannon!\""
msgstr "\"这可不是你爷爷那辈的 .50 口径手炮！\""

#: .\snippets.json
msgid "\"Nice pistol!  Which trigger fires the flamer?\""
msgstr "\"好手枪！哪个扳机是发射火焰喷射器的？\""

#: .\snippets.json
msgid "\"Why in the name of fuck did I slap a crossbow on this handgun.\""
msgstr "\"我他妈到底为啥要把弩装在这把手枪上。\""
